p: Toluene extraction was also carried out, resulting in a cleaner extract and with a slightly higher content of compound 181 than EtOH extracts. In addition, these extracts were found to be active, with better efficacy against the W2 clone. EC values were: Togo, 2.77 µg/mL; Costa Rica, 0.70 µg/mL; and Belize, 0.65 µg/mL.
